OL,3,CFive nurseries saved from closure
OL,4,Cfollowing outcry from parents
OL,6,FFive nurseries in the Scottish Borders
OL,7,Fhave been saved from closure - for now
OL,8,F- following an outcry from parents
OL,9,Fover the last month.
OL,11,FScottish Borders Council called a
OL,12,Fmeeting to review its plans to
OL,13,Ftemporarily close five nurseries in
OL,14,FCockburnspath, Ednam, Oxton, Yetholm
OL,15,Fand Walkerburn for the next education
OL,16,Fyear on 9 May 2025.
