OL,3,CFive nurseries saved from closure
OL,4,Cfollowing outcry from parents
OL,6,FDespite U-turning on their original
OL,7,Fdecision, last month the local
OL,8,Fauthority cited a reduction in the
OL,9,Fnumber of children using the
OL,10,Ffacilities and the need to save money.
OL,12,FMore than 30 parents in Cockburnspath,
OL,13,Fnear Eyemouth, took part in a protest
OL,14,Fagainst the proposals on 2 May 2025.
