OL,3,CFive nurseries saved from closure
OL,4,Cfollowing outcry from parents
OL,6,FFollowing the announced plans, parent
OL,7,FPaul Fulton, from Save Channelkirk
OL,8,FNursery Group, said: "(I am) slightly
OL,9,Fconcerned by the fact that they're
OL,10,Flooking to potentially rush through a
OL,11,Fnew and different way forward for the
OL,12,Fschools, for the nursery.
OL,14,F"It's not really been done anywhere
OL,15,Felse in Scotland. So the fact they're
OL,16,Ftrying to push that through in the
OL,17,Fnext three months is very worrying."
