OL,7,FWestruther and Fountainhall nurseries
OL,8,Fare also being reviewed in
OL,9,Fconsultation with the public.
OL,11,FCllr Julie Pirone, from Scottish
OL,12,FBorders Council, said: "Co-location is
OL,13,Fwhere you put children from different
OL,14,Fages into the same class group
OL,15,Feffectively.
OL,17,F"We already see that in all our rural
OL,18,Fprimary schools where you can have
OL,19,Fprimary one, two, three or four.
